Package com.billiards

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ball
    Represents a ball.
    Billiards
    This class is the Backbone of the entire application.
    GameProcessor
    Represents the game rules logic for an 8-Ball Pool game
    LaunchMenu
    Represents the launch menu of the game.
    Player
    Represents a player, holds the necessary data for a single player.
    PoolStick
    Represents the pool stick that is used to strike the cueball.
    SettingsMenu
    Represents a settings menu, allows you to change various settings from fps, to control settings, music and can play Akashs music genesis project by clicking "Surround Sound"
